1056
00:59:02,240 --> 00:59:03,930
Rym: Don't just go along or don't just passively think.

1057
00:59:03,970 --> 00:59:05,620
Rym: Like, actively interrogate yourself.

1058
00:59:06,040 --> 00:59:07,805
Rym: This is literal introspection.

1059
00:59:08,748 --> 00:59:09,851
Rym: Do I want to do this?

1060
00:59:11,234 --> 00:59:13,100
Rym: What do I expect this to be like?

1061
00:59:14,741 --> 00:59:18,152
Rym: What is the likelihood that my expectations will match reality?

1062
00:59:19,115 --> 00:59:20,860
