1112
01:01:58,770 --> 01:02:02,810
Scott: But, you know, so it's like you can quit.

1113
01:02:02,890 --> 01:02:05,950
Scott: You know, don't just stay in your job because you got some routine or something.

1114
01:02:06,350 --> 01:02:14,110
Rym: Well, part of what the part of the with in terms of real things is it comes down to to have you made affirmative commitments or not, because it's a very different situation.

1115
01:02:14,691 --> 01:02:19,630
