01:03:31,779 --> 01:03:32,389
Scott: That's a good one.

1143
01:03:33,071 --> 01:03:36,770
Rym: Or I accidentally scheduled my own wedding that same day and didn't tell anyone.

1144
01:03:37,870 --> 01:03:37,971
Scott: Right.

1145
01:03:37,991 --> 01:03:41,490
Scott: Or it's like, hey, let's start a family and make babies together.

1146
01:03:41,691 --> 01:03:42,930
Scott: Actually, I'm going to just run away.

1147
01:03:43,211 --> 01:03:45,670
Rym: It's like, you know, that's what I was going to bring up earlier.

1148
01:03:45,771 --> 01:03:48,350
Rym: If you can just bail on anything like that, just bail on, I don't know, kids.

1149
01:03:49,670 --> 01:03:49,851
Scott: Right.

1150
01:03:49,911 --> 01:03:55,030
Scott: It's like, you know, there are ways, you know, to go about, you know, you've crossed the line of no return.

1151
01:03:55,130 --> 01:04:00,850
Scott: There are ways to, you know, divorce and do whatever, you know, in a way that is, you know, healthy.

1152
01:04:01,071 --> 01:04:01,352
Scott: Right.

1153
01:04:01,412 --> 01:04:05,370
Scott: And does not cause lots of damage and whatnot to other human beings.

1154
01:04:05,690 --> 01:04:10,669
Rym: Well, like if we had to bail on a convention we'd committed to for a valid reason or even an invalid reason.

1155
